arStrings.szText: "Can you lead me to the Tree of Whispers?"
Your question shows a profound ignorance of this place.
Not mean or cruel but matter-of-factly. Like a scientist trying to explain to a layman.
You cannot be led to the Tree. It reveals itself only to those it considers worthy. Even I cannot speak to it without its permission.
Not mean or cruel but matter-of-factly. Like a scientist trying to explain to a layman.
